OL,3,COpponents fear desalination plant
OL,4,Ccould harm the environment
OL,6,FOpponents say a desalination plant,
OL,7,Fwhich South West Water wants to build
OL,8,Fin St Austell Bay, Cornwall, will
OL,9,Fdestroy marine life and damage the
OL,10,Fenvironment.
OL,12,FThe company wants to build the plant -
OL,13,Fwhich will turn seawater into drinking
OL,14,Fwater - at Par, to help boost water
OL,15,Fsupplies in the Duchy.
