OL,6,FJohn Elkington, a member of the
OL,7,Fdesalination information group said:"I
OL,8,Fdon't think we've got to the bottom of
OL,9,Fwhat this will mean to the
OL,10,Fenvironment, everyone is very keen to
OL,11,Ftell me how important it is, but I
OL,12,Fdon't think they've been upfront on
OL,13,Fthe evidence on what the environmental
OL,14,Fimpact of desalination actually is."
