OL,6,F"What South West Water are doing is
OL,7,Fplaying catch up, on all the years
OL,8,Fwhen insufficient work has been done
OL,9,Fto cope with the challenges that are
OL,10,Fahead, and I don't underestimate
OL,11,Fthose, climate change is real and
OL,12,Fwe're going to get drier summers, but
OL,13,Fwe will also get rain in the winter
OL,14,Fand we could be doing more to store
OL,15,Fit."
