OL,6,FThe first phase of the plan will see a
OL,7,Fsmaller plant in five shipping
OL,8,Fcontainer sized units delivered and
OL,9,Fconnected to existing infrastructure
OL,10,Fwhile further plans are developed for
OL,11,Fa much larger plant.
OL,13,FSouth West Water says the first phase
OL,14,Fwill be capable of producing between
OL,15,F2.5 and 5 million litres of clean
OL,16,Fdrinking water daily when needed.
