OL,3,COpponents fear desalination plant
OL,4,Ccould harm the environment
OL,6,FDavid Harris, South West Water's
OL,7,FDrought and Resilience Director, said:
OL,8,F"Desalination is one part of our wider
OL,9,F#125 million investment plan to
OL,10,Fincrease the water resources available
OL,11,Fin Cornwall by 45% and in Devon by 30%
OL,12,Fby 2025 to break the cycle of drought.
OL,14,F"Regulators are encouraging water
OL,15,Fcompanies to develop supplies that are
OL,16,Fresilient to the impacts of climate
OL,17,Fchange, and desalination allows us to
OL,18,Fprotect supplies across our region in
OL,19,Fthe face of a changing climate in ways
OL,20,Fthat more common interventions cannot.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
