OL,6,F"We share the passion that many locals
OL,7,Fhave shown to protect the sensitive
OL,8,Fmarine environment in St Austell Bay
OL,9,Fand this month's events will provide
OL,10,Fus with an opportunity to continue
OL,11,Fdemonstrating that we are doing
OL,12,Feverything we can to minimise any
OL,13,Fimpact we have to marine habitats."
