OL,6,FMaureen was one of the visitors to an
OL,7,Finformation event in Lostwithiel, her
OL,8,Ffather worked at Par Docks for many
OL,9,Fyears. She said: "There's been so much
OL,10,Fnegative talk about it from local
OL,11,Fpeople, I just wanted to find out for
OL,12,Fmyself and find out why we need a
OL,13,Fdesalination plant in view of the
OL,14,Fwater that is pouring from the sky at
OL,15,Fthe moment."
